                     <interp inst="t18151025-109-person931" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . It was my duty to seal the Knightsbridge bag, and I have no doubt, but that I did so on the 14th of July.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18151025-109-person932">
                  JOHN 
                  SMITH ATLEE
               <interp inst="t18151025-109-person932" type="surname" value="SMITH ATLEE"></interp>
