                     <interp inst="t18151025-109-person932" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was employed in the Post Office at Knightsbridge, on the 14th of July, I received the bag as usual, on its arrival. There is but one deliverer at Knightsbridge. I, and a person, named Lowndes, sorted the letters; I sorted all that came to my share, and gave them to Jannaway, the deliverer.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18151025-109-person933">
