                  </persName>
            . I am the deliverer of letters at Knightsbridge. I was on duty on the 14th of July. I knew very well where Mrs. Simpson lived. If I had had a letter for that day, I should certainly have delivered it.</p>
               <p>MRS. 
               <persName id="t18151025-109-person936">
                  JANE 
                  SIMPSON
               <interp inst="t18151025-109-person936" type="surname" value="SIMPSON"></interp>
